reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on May 9, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Heavy Duty Stand -- Orbi RBS750 Satellite Fits Perfectly
reviews.reviewText: Perfect for my Orbi satellite. Screws mounting Orbi to stand have updated and screw tightly to the base plate and Orbi without needing washers. Reviewers indicated the Orbi anchor screws they received passed through the baseplate. That's fixed.Mounted this behind my smart TV for additional ethernet wiring for wired streaming devices, TiVo, and for vastly improved WiFi to my smart TV.I mounted the stand on the wall using picture mount anchors which are less damaging to my wall. I used a couple round felt pads on the portion of the plate which is against the wall to avoid damaging wall and to provide a more level surface for the Orbi. I wrapped the Orbi A/C cord around the handy winding posts and plugged the cord into the Orbi without problems. I then hand tightened the plate-to-Orbi anchor screws into the Orbi. the holes line up perfectly between the Orbi and the stand.I now have a secure out-of-sight mounting platform and improved WiFi from my satellite. Delighted with this mounting system. Highly recommended.

reviews.reviewTitle: Recomendables - Soportes para Netgear Orbi RBK753S
reviews.reviewText: Los soportes son de aluminio de 2.5mm, en color natural que combina con el diseño del enrutrador y los satélites. El kit incluye dos soportes, incluye tornillos y taquetes para fijarlos a la pared, y cuatro pares de tornillos (dos pasos de cuerda diferente - M4x10 y 32x3/8" -) para fijar los equipos.Elegí esta marca y modelo por: precio, color, y por que el diseño del soporte tiene recortes para ventilar los equipos por la parte inferior.Tienen las dimensiones exactas, no se doblan o mueven con el peso ya montados El diseño de los soportes mantiene los equipos separados de la pared, incluyen elementos con recortes del mismo aluminio para enredar los cables de alimentación y/o ethernet y que no queden sueltos.El único detalle son las perforaciones de los tornillos para sujetar los equipos, son del diámetro de la cabeza de los tornillos, para solucionar esto tuve que colocar rondanas pequeñas.En general fueron una buena elección, por lo que los recomiendo.

reviews.reviewTitle: Overall sturdy quality but one major flaw
reviews.reviewText: The stand itself has smooth edges and nice finish to it. Certainly strong enough to hold the RBR850, BUT, as seen in the picture, the provided screws head are way too small that it just went right through the hole. Although I received it, I cannot use it yet because I need to go to a hardware store to pick up two washers.... That's too bad.
